  National  Institute  of  Mental 

Health  and  Neuro  Sciences  is  really  doing  a  wonderful  service  to  the  nation.    A 

common man without any financial help can go to that hospital and get treatment.  

I will request the hon. Minister to take some initiative to improve and create more 

facilities in the hospital.  I request the Central Government to establish more ICUs, 

more ventilator facilities in this hospital so that a common man who is in dire need 

of assistance from the hospital could be provided with the necessary help. 

 

 THE  MINISTER  OF  HEALTH  AND  FAMILY  WELFARE  (SHRI 

